Name: Lesser Kao Rune
Types: Rune
Components: Basic Kao Rune, Level 1 Spell Slot
Description: This rune symbolizes ill intent, lasting suffering, and misfortune. It is commonly known as the rune of curses, allowing those who wield it the ability to inflict calamity upon their foes.SPACESPACEWhile wearing or using an item imbued with this rune, you gain the following feature.SPACECurse of IllnessSPACEAs an action, you inflict horrible disease upon a target within DISTANCE15-30DISTANCE feet of you. The target must succeed on a Constitution saving throw or become poisoned for TIME2-4TIME rounds. While poisoned, they take an additional POTENCY2-3POTENCYd4 poison damage whenever they take damage. A creature that succeeds on its saving throw is immune to this effect for the next 24 hours.SPACESPACEYou may use this rune a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus before its magic is depleted. The rune will recharge from ambient magic as you complete a long rest.